                     <p className="text-xs text-emerald-600/80 leading-relaxed font-medium">检测到“Vegan Lip Gloss”搜索热度上升，建议本周增加相关关键词的文章发布。</p>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div className="p-5 bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl border border-blue-100">
